# Cursor AI Rules for ibexa/admin-ui

## Git Workflow - LOCAL CHANGES ONLY

**CRITICAL: All changes MUST remain local. DO NOT push or create PRs automatically.**

### NEVER DO:
- ❌ `git push` or `git push origin <branch>`
- ❌ `gh pr create` or any PR creation commands
- ❌ `git push --force`
- ❌ Automatic merging or rebasing with remote branches

### ALLOWED:
- ✅ Local file changes
- ✅ `git status`, `git diff`, `git log`
- ✅ `git add` and `git commit` (local commits only)
- ✅ `git checkout -b <branch>` (local branches only)
- ✅ Running tests locally
- ✅ Showing diffs and status

### User Control:
The user will manually push and create PRs when ready.

See CLAUDE.md and MIGRATION_RULES.md for complete documentation.
